	<Title>
		Burned by fun in the sun?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;If you have a sunburn, the damage is already done. But you can ease the discomfort: 1. Take ibuprofen (Advil, Motrin, others) or aspirin for pain. 2. Apply cold compresses or take a cool bath. 3. Apply a moisturizing cream or creams containing aloe or hydrocortisone. 4. If blisters form, don&apos;t break them. You can lightly cover them with gauze.&lt;/p&gt;
